description:
This is a 32 minute workout called '30 minute Full Body Strength Training with Dumbbells' from the channel Kaleigh Cohen Strength.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Warrior Workout and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Join me as we tone and strengthen our upper body, lower body, and abs with this strength session! This is a seriosuly rocking workout that will help you build total body strength! Grab some heavy dumbbells and let's get STRONG!

FULL BODY STRENGTH TRAINING DUMBBELL WORKOUT STRUCTURE AND EXERCISES
MUSCLES TARGETED:  BACK, CHEST, BICEPS, TRICEPS, SHOULDERS, GLUTES, HAMSTRINGS, QUADS, AND ABS.
EQUIPMENT NEEDED
- DUMBBELLS- I used a range from 10lbs to 45lbs
- EXERCISE MAT
OPTIONAL EQUIPMENT

STRUCTURE
10 TOTAL EXERCISES
REPEAT TWO TIMES THROUGH 
WORK: 50 SECONDS REST: 30 SECONDS

EXERCISE LIST 
- SQUAT WITH ALTERNATING SIDE LATERAL LEG LIFT
- REAR DELT FLYES
- SUMO SQUAT W/ HOLD AT BOTTOM
- CLOSE GRIP SHOULDER PRESS
- BICEP CURLS - NEUTRAL AND WIDE
- SUMO RDL
- GLUTE BRIDGE WALKOUTS
- CHEST FLYES
- MARCHING CRUNCH AND CLAP
- REVERSE CRUNCH

Thanks for working out with me! It's always better to work out with a friend!

Kaleigh
